article.headline: Bashir scores 28 in Monmouth's 63-51 win against Seton Hall
article.description: — Abdi Bashir Jr. had 28 points in Monmouth's 63-51 win over Seton Hall on Saturday.
article.linkText: Bashir scores 28 in Monmouth's 63-51 win against Seton Hall
article.story: NEWARK, N.J. -- — Abdi Bashir Jr. had 28 points in Monmouth's 63-51 win over Seton Hall on Saturday. Bashir shot 11 for 19, including 6 for 9 from beyond the arc for the Hawks (1-8). Jack Collins scored 13 points while shooting 4 for 12 (3 for 11 from 3-point range) and 2 of 3 from the free-throw line and added five rebounds. Jaret Valencia went 5 of 8 from the field to finish with 11 points. Isaiah Coleman led the Pirates (4-4) in scoring, finishing with 20 points. Chaunce Jenkins added 12 points. Bashir helped Monmouth pull away with 10 second-half points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
